'''豪尔赫·保罗·阿格斯迪诺·门德斯'''（{{lang-pt|Jorge Paulo Agostinho Mendes}}，{{bd|1966年|1月7日}}），是一名出生于[[里斯本|里斯本]]的[[葡萄牙|葡萄牙]]籍足球经理人，他是[[葡萄牙足球协会|葡萄牙足球协会]]的注册经理人<ref>[http://www.fifa.com/aboutfifa/organisation/footballgovernance/playeragents/association=por.html Players' Agents List] {{Wayback|url=http://www.fifa.com/aboutfifa/organisation/footballgovernance/playeragents/association=por.html |date=20150402154429 }}, fifa.com, retrieved 30 March 2015</ref>，也是1996年成立的经纪公司[[GestiFute|GestiFute]]之负责人<ref>[http://www.gestifute.com/gestifute/quemsomos.php "GestiFute: About Us"] {{Webarchive|url=http://arquivo.pt/wayback/20090723235400/http://www.gestifute.com/gestifute/quemsomos.php |date=2009-07-23 }} Retrieved 2010-08-02.</ref>。门德斯被视为足球经纪界最具影响力之人物，旗下球星及球圈名人包括[[穆里尼奧|穆里尼奧]]、[[斯科拉里|斯科拉里]]、[[卡洛斯|卡洛斯]]、[[撒布隆撒|撒布隆撒]]、[[安德森·路易斯·迪·阿布努·奥利維拉|安德森]]、[[法比奥·科恩特朗|法比奥·科恩特朗]]、[[佩佩|佩佩]]、[[迪马利亚|迪马利亚]]、[[克里斯蒂亚諾·罗纳尔多|克里斯蒂亚諾·罗纳尔多]]、[[法尔考|法尔考]]、[[迭戈·科斯塔|迭戈·科斯塔]]<ref>{{cite news|last1=Burt|first1=Jason|title=Diego Costa: I take things to limit but I did nothing wrong|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/teams/chelsea/11381605/Diego-Costa-I-take-things-to-limit-but-I-did-nothing-wrong.html|accessdate=1 February 2015|work=The Daily Telegraph|date=31 January 2015|archive-date=2018-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180629162426/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/teams/chelsea/11381605/Diego-Costa-I-take-things-to-limit-but-I-did-nothing-wrong.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>、[[布拉希米|布拉希米]]、[[卡瓦略|卡瓦略]]、[[纳尼|纳尼]]、[[夸雷斯马|夸雷斯马]]、[[伊尔马兹|伊尔马兹]]、[[穆蒂尼奥|穆蒂尼奥]]、[[哈梅斯·罗德里格斯|哈梅斯·罗德里格斯]]、[[德赫亚|德赫亚]]及[[巴尔德斯|巴尔德斯]]等<ref name="mendestel">[http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/10085617/Monaco-break-the-bank-with-110m-spree-and-send-out-warning-to-Europes-giants.html "Monaco break the bank with £110m spree and send out warning to Europe's giants"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/10085617/Monaco-break-the-bank-with-110m-spree-and-send-out-warning-to-Europes-giants.html |date=20150926003255 }} by Oliver Brown, ''[[The_Daily_Telegraph|The Daily Telegraph]]'', 28 May 2013</ref>。门德斯是如今球坛影响力最大，也是最被人熟悉的一位经理人<ref name="mendestel"/><ref>[http://www.marca.com/2013/05/28/en/football/international_football/1369775727.html "Falcao on the verge of Monaco move"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.marca.com/2013/05/28/en/football/international_football/1369775727.html |date=20160303220021 }}, ''[[Marca_(newspaper)|Marca]]'', 28 May 2013</ref> 。

2012年12月在[[迪拜|迪拜]]举行的[[环球足球奖|环球足球奖]]中<ref>[http://www.globesoccer.com/awards/walloffame/#filter=.winners2012 "And the winner is..."] {{Wayback|url=http://www.globesoccer.com/awards/walloffame/#filter=.winners2012 |date=20160107205956 }} Globe Soccer Awards website</ref>，门德斯旗下的法尔考贏得年度最佳球员奖，其所属的[[马德里竞技|马德里竞技]]亦获得年度最佳球队，而时任[[皇家马德里|皇家马德里]]的主教练[[穆里尼奥|穆里尼奥]]亦被封年度最佳教练。门德斯则是连续3年荣获年度最佳经理人之荣誉<ref>[http://online.wsj.com/article/SB10001424127887323482504578225474079309426.html "How to Own a Team Without Buying One"] {{Wayback|url=http://online.wsj.com/article/SB10001424127887323482504578225474079309426.html |date=20130729035533 }} by Gabriele Marcotti, ''[[The_Wall_Street_Journal|The Wall Street Journal]]'', 6 January 2013</ref>。

